{"tid":693951,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［新手求助] 話說我兩個禮拜前領養咗對驚青貓","createTime":"2018-06-08T02:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T14:43:51.000Z","uid":18691,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c25217ffc0f83df4fe0c33ba5efed3e37177e201","tid":693951,"uid":18691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T02:09:39.000Z","msg":"新手領養咗一對4歲成貓兩個禮拜 (好奇主子同懶主子）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩位主子都好慢熱好怕羞 <br />\n初初黎到就係困籠 <br />\n過咗4日左右之後 我地見佢地都好定 冇問到義工就開咗籠個門比佢地出黎自由活動<br />\n<br />\n出咗黎之後就一齊哩咗喺疏化底幾日 <br />\n好奇主子過咗幾日就轉咗位 佔據咗電視後面 <br />\n佢有時都會裝吓我地 <br />\n但係我地餵佢 佢就仲未肯喺我志火面前食住<br />\n<br />\n懶主子就仍然住喺疏化底 點都唔出黎 有時連人都唔望<br />\n奴才好好奇主子喺夜晚同埋屋企冇人嗰陣係點活動 <br />\n於是裝咗個ip cam觀察<br />\n<br />\n夜晚個廳冇人個時佢地就會出黎活動 <br />\n好奇主子由初初隔10分鐘先出黎 到依家過一分鐘就出黎<br />\n<br />\n有時我地入咗房好奇主子已經會走出黎 <br />\n見到我地又會驚 哩返入去 <br />\n佢出咗黎之後我地行返出廳 佢就會進入戒備狀態同伏底 但又唔會跑走<br />\n點樣先可以令主子放底戒心 同埋肯喺我地面前食野呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a5f3222fc20ce59db05cca8471d3221c34ce4c6","tid":693951,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":27,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T02:11:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d56f29d5d77773a8ee4dc06839694b1f3cd117f8","tid":693951,"uid":12839,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T02:17:24.000Z","msg":"一定要當佢地無到，完全當睇佢唔到就得<br />\n佢地好快就會出黎"},{"pid":"ec885fa4697a153644476ba6422b6ccfb8928391","tid":693951,"uid":47819,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T02:19:20.000Z","msg":"試下用手餵d小食<br />\n促進感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n慢慢慣左就可以趁佢地食嘢果時摸下頭》身〉試下抱"},{"pid":"3315088f263d3a059ce159170e0998c7915ae182","tid":693951,"uid":157197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T02:23:43.000Z","msg":"相呢相呢"},{"pid":"28077e267ce9dd8a3098e6c689705fc6eb8d729b","tid":693951,"uid":18691,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"3315088f263d3a059ce159170e0998c7915ae182","tid":693951,"uid":157197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T02:23:43.000Z","msg":"相呢相呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T04:05:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/08/120506_b31f56a497426865a3d9c21234293932.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F08%2F120506_b31f56a497426865a3d9c21234293932.png&h=0c32f36b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張係放咗出黎第二日左右 驚驚青青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b03c9028604a58bfd4ffc1d6baa99e91e4a9208","tid":693951,"uid":18691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d56f29d5d77773a8ee4dc06839694b1f3cd117f8","tid":693951,"uid":12839,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T02:17:24.000Z","msg":"一定要當佢地無到，完全當睇佢唔到就得<br />\n佢地好快就會出黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T04:06:47.000Z","msg":"淨係換糧換水換貓砂 其他時間唔好理佢地？<br />\n擺唔擺長糧好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b7951b42ce93a6b8c5e98a83c1f36a6add0b99","tid":693951,"uid":103823,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T04:10:19.000Z","msg":"我都領養咗隻4歲貓仔<br />\n唔好望佢 唔好理佢<br />\n佢幾個星期就會自在啲喺屋企四圍行<br />\n<br />\n而家過咗兩個月<br />\n佢當咗自己係大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8607b09a5bbeb9c6a275b086a5c7b95aa2b604","tid":693951,"uid":18691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec885fa4697a153644476ba6422b6ccfb8928391","tid":693951,"uid":47819,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T02: